      528.07,
      533.93,
      566.23
    ],
    "text": "Showers or thundershowers will occur at a few places in Western, Sabaragamuwa and North-western provinces and in Galle, Matara, Kandy, Nuwara-Eliya and Mannar districts after 2.00 p.m.",
